OL,3,CYoung people more sick now than in
OL,4,Cprevious generations, study finds
OL,6,FThe team warned that the higher
OL,7,Fprevalence of ill health in more
OL,8,Frecent generations "suggests that more
OL,9,Fyears in total may be spent living in
OL,10,Fpoor health" than experienced by
OL,11,Fprevious generations.
