PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1779437195
OL,3,CYoung people more sick now than in
OL,4,Cprevious generations, study finds
OL,6,FThey concluded: "While several
OL,7,Fmechanisms could explain the
OL,8,Fgenerational health drift, evidence
OL,9,Ffrom the British birth cohorts
OL,10,Fsuggests that more recent cohorts are
OL,11,Fexperiencing an earlier onset of poor
OL,12,Fhealth for several outcomes,
OL,13,Fparticularly obesity and mental ill
OL,14,Fhealth.
OL,26,@nD@QOU
